/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"BiographyWiki\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Biography\/Wiki<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Zaira Wasim was born on<strong> 23 October 2000 (18 years old; age as in 2018).\u00a0<\/strong><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_685\" style=\"width: 371px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Childhood-Picture.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-685\" class=\"wp-image-685 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Childhood-Picture.png\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim Childhood Picture\" width=\"361\" height=\"339\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Childhood-Picture.png 361w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Childhood-Picture-300x282.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 361px) 100vw, 361px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-685\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim&#8217;s childhood picture<\/p><\/div>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Birthday.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-698 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Birthday.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim Birthday\" width=\"700\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Birthday.jpg 700w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Birthday-300x214.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>She shot to fame for her portrayal of the role of the<strong> child version of Geeta Phogat in the movie &#8220;Dangal.&#8221;<\/strong> Since then there has been no looking back for Zaira Wasim. Her performance in the movie was commercially and critically acclaimed.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Physical Appearance<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim.-.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-687 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim.-.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim\" width=\"352\" height=\"600\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim.-.jpg 352w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim.--176x300.jpg 176w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 352px) 100vw, 352px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Zaira <strong>5\u2032 1&#8243;\u00a0<\/strong><strong>tall<\/strong><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>&amp; weighs approx <strong>50 kg<\/strong>. She has\u00a0<strong>black eyes, black hair,<\/strong>\u00a0and <strong>fair complexion<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family_Caste_Boyfriend\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Family, Caste &amp; Boyfriend<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Zaira Wasim<\/strong> was born and brought up in a <strong>Muslim family<\/strong> with <strong>Islam ethnicity in Hawal, Downtown, Srinagar, Jammu, and Kashmir<\/strong>. She is a <strong>half Kashmiri<\/strong> and<strong> half Punjabi<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim..jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-699 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim..jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim\" width=\"588\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim..jpg 588w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim.-300x255.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 588px) 100vw, 588px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>She lives with her parents and one younger<strong>\u00a0brother, Zoraiz Wasim.<\/strong>\u00a0Her<strong> father, Zahid Wasim,<\/strong> is an <strong>Executive Manager of the Jammu and Kashmir Bank<\/strong> while her <strong>mother, Zarqa Wasim,<\/strong> is a <strong>teacher.<\/strong> She is very close to her father.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_689\" style=\"width: 329px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-parents.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-689\" class=\"wp-image-689 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-parents.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim Parents\" width=\"319\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-parents.jpg 319w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-parents-191x300.jpg 191w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 319px) 100vw, 319px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-689\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim with her parents<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_690\" style=\"width: 561px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Brother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-690\" class=\"wp-image-690 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Brother.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim Brother\" width=\"551\" height=\"539\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Brother.jpg 551w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Brother-300x293.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Brother-65x65.jpg 65w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 551px) 100vw, 551px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-690\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim with her brother<\/p><\/div>\n<p>She is <strong>single<\/strong>\u00a0as of now and not dating anyone.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Career<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Zaira Wasim completed her <strong>schooling<\/strong> from\u00a0<strong>St. Paul&#8217;s International Academy, Sonwar, Srinagar, Jammu &amp; Kashmir and\u00a0Jammu\u2019s Heritage School, Jammu &amp; Kashmir<\/strong>.\u00a0Since her childhood, she was a <strong>brilliant student<\/strong>. She scored <strong>92% marks<\/strong> in <strong>10th board examination.<\/strong> As of 2018, she was\u00a0<strong>pursuing secondary education<\/strong> from\u00a0<strong>Heritage School, Jammu.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Before entering the Bollywood, she had acted in <strong>two television commercials-<\/strong> &#8220;<strong>Microsoft Lumia&#8221;\u00a0<\/strong>and<strong>\u00a0&#8220;Tata Sky<\/strong>.&#8221; In <strong>2016,<\/strong> she started her <strong>career<\/strong> in <strong>Bollywood<\/strong> with the superhit Bollywood movie &#8220;<strong>Dangal&#8221;<\/strong> in which she played the childhood character of Indian sportsgirl <strong>Geeta Phogat<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_692\" style=\"width: 650px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-in-Dangal..jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-692\" class=\"wp-image-692 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-in-Dangal..jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim in Dangal\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-in-Dangal..jpg 640w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-in-Dangal.-300x225.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-692\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim in Dangal<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In <strong>2017,<\/strong> she appeared in the movie\u00a0<strong>&#8220;Secret Superstar.&#8221;<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>On 30 June 2019, she announced her disassociation from the glamour world citing religious reasons.<\/p>\n<blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram