 Child Actress (2017)<\/strong> for <strong>Dangal.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Filmfare Award<\/strong> for <strong>Best Actress (Critics) (2018)<\/strong> for <strong>Secret Superstar.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Star Screen Award<\/strong> for the <strong>Most Promising Newcomer (2017)<\/strong> for <strong>Secret Superstar.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>National Child Award<\/strong> for <strong>Exceptional Achievement (2017)<\/strong> for <strong>Secret Superstar.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Lux Golden Rose Award<\/strong> for <strong>Emerging Beauty of the Year<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>(2017)<\/strong> for <strong>Secret Superstar.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_697\" style=\"width: 762px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-receives-National-Film-Award-for-Best-Supporting-Actress-for-Dangal.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-697\" class=\"wp-image-697 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-receives-National-Film-Award-for-Best-Supporting-Actress-for-Dangal.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim receiving National Film Award for Best Supporting Actress for Dangal\" width=\"752\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-receives-National-Film-Award-for-Best-Supporting-Actress-for-Dangal.jpg 752w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-receives-National-Film-Award-for-Best-Supporting-Actress-for-Dangal-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 752px) 100vw, 752px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-697\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim receiving National Film Award for Best Supporting Actress for Dangal<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_11963\" style=\"width: 645px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11963\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11963\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-1.jpg\" alt=\"Zara Wasim receiving National Award\" width=\"635\" height=\"584\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-1.jpg 635w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-1-300x276.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 635px) 100vw, 635px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-11963\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zara Wasim receiving National Award<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Controversies<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2016, Zaira Wasim&#8217;s pictures with hair trimmed went viral on the internet. She was criticized and trolled by radical Muslims for having been un-Islamic by acting in a Hindi film.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In 2016, Zaira had a <strong>controversial meeting with the then Jammu &amp; Kashmir Chief Minister Mehbooba Mufti<\/strong> whereby Mufti had portrayed Zaira as the role model of the Kashmiri youth. Later, Zaira apologized on her social media accounts. However, deleted this apology after some time and added another open letter clarifying everything. Moreover, the subsequent post was yet again deleted.\n<p><div id=\"attachment_700\" style=\"width: 657px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-with-Mehbooba-Mufti-Sayeed.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-700\" class=\"wp-image-700 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-with-Mehbooba-Mufti-Sayeed.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim with Mehbooba Mufti Sayeed\" width=\"647\" height=\"404\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-with-Mehbooba-Mufti-Sayeed.jpg 647w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-with-Mehbooba-Mufti-Sayeed-300x187.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 647px) 100vw, 647px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-700\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim with Mehbooba Mufti Sayeed<\/p><\/div><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_11966\" style=\"width: 693px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11966\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11966\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-controversy-1.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim's deleted Facebook post\" width=\"683\" height=\"495\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-controversy-1.jpg 683w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-controversy-1-300x217.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 683px) 100vw, 683px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-11966\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim&#8217;s deleted Facebook post<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_11968\" style=\"width: 677px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11968\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11968\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Mehbooba-Mufti-controversy.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"667\" height=\"343\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Mehbooba-Mufti-controversy.jpg 667w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Mehbooba-Mufti-controversy-300x154.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 667px) 100vw, 667px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-11968\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim&#8217;s subsequent post which was also deleted<\/p><\/div>\n<ul>\n<li>On January 2017, the\u00a0former Minister of Youth Affairs and Sports <strong>Vijay Goel<\/strong> tweeted that <strong>&#8221;This painting tells a story similar to @zairawasim. Pinjra torh kar hamari betiyan barhne lagi hai aage <\/strong>(Our daughters are breaking out of their cages and moving forward)<strong> More power to our daughters!\u201d\u00a0<\/strong>In reply,\u00a0 Zaira tweeted <strong>&#8220;I feel I must disagree. I request you not to connect me to such a discourteous depiction. Women in hijab are beautiful and free. Moreover, the story depicted through this painting is not even remotely relevant to mine.&#8221;<\/strong> After that, Goel responded that Zaira had misunderstood his tweet and he appreciated her work and meant to discourage evil and patriarchal notions.\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Vijay-Goel-Tweets.png\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-704 size-full\" src=\"http:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Vijay-Goel-Tweets.png\" alt=\"Vijay Goel Tweets\" width=\"501\" height=\"478\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Vijay-Goel-Tweets.png 501w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Vijay-Goel-Tweets-300x286.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 501px) 100vw, 501px\" \/><\/a><\/li>\n<li>On 10 December 2017, she was molested on a Vistara flight from Delhi to Mumbai by a 39-year-old man, Vikas Sachdeva, a senior executive of a media and entertainment company. The same day, the Police arrested the accused of molesting her and booked him under section 354 (assault or criminal force to woman with intent to outrage her modesty) of IPC, and the Protection of Children from Sexual Offences Act (POCSO).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_11969\" style=\"width: 1073px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11969\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11969\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Vistara-controversy.jpg\" alt=\"Zaira Wasim's Vistara controversy\" width=\"1063\" height=\"397\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Vistara-controversy.jpg 1063w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Vistara-controversy-300x112.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Vistara-controversy-768x287.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/11\/Zaira-Wasim-Vistara-controversy-1024x382.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1063px) 100vw, 1063px\" \/><p id=\"caption-attachment-11969\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Zaira Wasim&#8217;s Vistara controversy<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Favourite_Things\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Favourite Things<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Zaira Wasim likes to listen to the song <strong>&#8220;Jealous&#8221;<\/strong> by <strong>Labrinth.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Her favourite singer is <strong>Ed Sheeran.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She has a liking for <strong>black<\/strong> colour.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Facts\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #800080\">Facts<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Zaira&#8217;s list of hobbies includes\u00a0breaking things, listening to songs, sleeping, reading, hanging out with friends, and playing with her pet cat.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Before acting in the movies, she appeared in the\u00a0<strong>TVC ads for Microsoft Lumia <\/strong>and<strong> Tata Sky.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Initially, Zaira Wasim&#8217;s parents did not agree with her decision to act in a\u00a0movie but Zaira&#8217;s school principle convinced them for letting her work in the movie &#8220;Dangal.&#8221;<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She did hard training\u00a0for the role of a wrestler.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>While preparing for the Dangal, Zaira stayed along with\u00a0<strong>Fatima Sana Shaikh,\u00a0Sanya Malhotra,\u00a0Suhani Bhatnagar<\/strong> at Aamir&#8217;s Khan&#8217;s old apartment in Mumbai for 6 months.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She is also the youth ambassador for the<strong> Bengaluru Midnight Marathon 2017.<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Wasim had social anxiety and self-esteem issues before she started her acting career.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>In an interview, she said that she is very<strong> shy and have a limited number of friends<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Zaira Wasim has some<strong> unusual and cranky likings<\/strong> like earthquakes, turbulent flights, wind turbines and\u00a0loves to break things.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Wasim loves to\u00a0listen to melodious songs and her all-time <strong>favourite song is Jealous by Labrinth<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She <strong>plays the guitar<\/strong> very well.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>She is a <strong>cat lover<\/strong>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Zaira Wasim is an Indian actress who is best known for her playing the role of childhood character of the Indian sportswoman\u00a0Geeta Phogat in the popular movie Dangal.\u00a0Let&#8217;s check out Zaira Wasim&#8217;s age, her personal life, career, and other interesting facts. Biography\/Wiki Zaira Wasim was born on 23 October 2000 (18 years old; age as in 2018).\u00a0 She shot to fame for her portrayal of the role of the child version of Geeta Phogat in the movie &#8220;Dangal.&#8221; Since then there has been no looking back for Zaira Wasim. Her performance in the movie was commercially and critically acclaimed. Physical <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":14,"featured_media":11956,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\